        </item>
        <item>
            <title>FUJIFILM instax mini 41 即影即有相机，经典复古外形 + 升级近拍体验</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/fujifilm-instax-mini-41/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=fujifilm-instax-mini-41</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/fujifilm-instax-mini-41/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 29 Apr 2025 09:20:43 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[fujifilm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm Instax]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Fujifilm instax mini 41]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Instax]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304992</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>富士推出新一代入门即影即有相机 instax mini 41，作为人气型号 mini 40 的后继机种，延续经典复古设计之余，亦针对用户需求进行多项升级。全新型号保留黑色与深银色的优雅外观，更以橙色作细节点缀，呈现出时尚与怀旧兼备的美学风格。作为一部入门即影即有相机，instax mini 41 特别适合入门新手用家，不论是日常生活、旅行出游、朋友聚会，皆可随时记录眼前场景，将回忆化为可触可感的实体照片。无论是作为日常配搭的小巧相机，抑或作为馈赠亲友的精致礼品，mini 41 都展现出其兼具实用与美感的独特魅力。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305013" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00647-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00647-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00647.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>保留经典外形，橙色点缀更 Sharp 醒</h2><p>instax mini 41 延续 mini 40 一贯的复古造型设计，机身以黑色与深银色作为主调，辅以细致的橙色线条点缀，呈现出低调而不失个性的时尚风格。整体外观揉合复古与现代感，无论是日常穿搭，还是出席特别场合时携带，都能轻松展现个人品味，成为造型焦点。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00640-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00640-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00640.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲延续 mini 40 复古造型设计</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00639-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00639-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00639.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00643-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00643-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00643.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲菲林计数器</p><p>相机下半部分采用细腻的纹理处理，不但增强握持手感，亦提高使用时的稳定性。无论是挂在胸前，还是单手操作拍摄，均具备良好的便携性与实用性，方便用户随时随地捕捉生活中的每一刻。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00638-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00638-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00638.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下半部分采用细腻的纹理处理</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00646-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00646-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00646.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲增强握持手感</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305008" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00642-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00642-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00642.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机背设有 thumb rest</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00644-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00644-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00644.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲惟一要弹是 mini 41 和上一代一样不设脚架孔</p><h2>近拍模式 + 自拍镜，影得埋自己都咁靓</h2><p class="" data-start="43" data-end="152">instax mini 41 特别新增了「近拍模式」，用户只需旋转镜头即可切换，无论拍摄特写物件或进行自拍，操作均十分简便。</p><p data-start="43" data-end="152"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305011" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00645-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00645-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00645.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p data-start="43" data-end="152"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305007" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00641-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00641-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00641.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-start="43" data-end="152">▲旋转镜头环即可调校至近摄模式</p><p class="" data-start="43" data-end="152">镜头旁设有小巧的自拍镜，方便用户即时确认画面构图，避免拍摄时出现脸部偏移或画面裁切不当的情况。</p><p data-start="43" data-end="152"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00636-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00636-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc00636.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305023" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc006382-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc006382-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/dsc006382.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲自拍镜</p><p class="" data-start="154" data-end="252">此外近拍模式亦支援「视差修正功能」，当用户透过取景框构图时，画面会自动对应实际成像范围，大大减少构图误差。即使是第一次使用即影即有相机，也能轻松掌握画面中心，拍出对位准确、效果理想的近距离照片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305024" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042574809-694x467.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="467" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042574809-694x467.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025042574809.jpg 1203w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/29/fujifilm-instax-mini-41/dc/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
